name: Klingendes Mayrhofen at the Europahaus
description:
Program: 
 
Wednesday, 10th May 2017
Mannsgesangverein Mayrhofen, Rainer_Quartett, Stualausmusig, Zithersolistin Kathrin
Wednesday, 17th May 2017
Mannsgesangverein Mayrhofen, Rainer_Quartett, The G'Firmtn, Zillertal School of Music, Accordionist Mario
Friday, 26th May 2017
Männergesangverein Mayrhofen, Rainer_Quartett, Schwendberger violin music, Reserlparty, Zithersolistin Kathrin
Saturday, 3rd June 2017
Männergesangverein Mayrhofen, folk songs with the church choir Tux, Brandberger Bläser, Höllwarth-Merk Hausmusik Hagen from Bavaria
Saturday, 17th June 2017
Mannsgesangverein Mayrhofen, Schwendberger violin music, Brandberger wind instruments, folk songs with the church choir Tux, Landesmusikschule Zillertal, accordionist Mario
Wednesday, 21st June 2017
Mannsgesangverein Mayrhofen, Reserlpartie, folk songs with the church choir Tux, Zithersolistin Kathrin
 Admission: with guest card € 8,00 without guest card € 10,00
Free choice of seats!
